                                "byte_start": 92684,
                                "byte_stop": 136361,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court in No. 00-203, United States versus Cleveland Indians Baseball Company will be announced by Justice Ginsburg."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 10.908,
                        "stop": 216.189,
